I'm in a great mood, I got on the scale this morning to find that I've lost 25 pounds since I started working out and watching what I eat.&nbsp; 

To celebrate, I did the only logical thing that I could possibly do, after working out this morning, I went to chinese buffet for lunch.&nbsp; So ok, tomorrow I'll have only lost 24 pounds, but I'll make that up later. :)&nbsp; 


And my therapist is very happy with the weight loss and the changing of my life style.&nbsp; He pointed out that as I was talking about the weight loss and the working out, my entire attitude and demeanor changed.&nbsp; He said I was smiling and happy and looked good.&nbsp; I couldn't help but smile even more as he said that.&nbsp; :)

Anyway, off to put away some stuff i bought and off to do some straigtening.&nbsp; ciao!
